Vicia ervilia

   [17507.jpg]
   Authority (L.) Willd.
   Family Magnoliopsida:Rosidae:Fabales:Leguminosae
   Synonyms
   Common names bitter vetch, lentil vetch, pigeon‚s pea, French erse,
   lenteja bastarda, lentille bâtarde, pois de pigeon, kirsannah,
   kuyewandou, Linsenwicke, ervilha de pombo, erven, erfva, erve, orobo,
   erb, pesette, ervum, alarceña, alcarceña, alcarraceña, alcaruna,
   alliez, alverja, alverjana, arveja, capogirlo, cicerchia, comin, er,
   eros, erp, ers, erse, Ervenlinse, Ervenwicke, ervil, ervilier, ervilla,
   ervilliere, ervo, ervos, Eselsohren, essez, faux orobe, fregellini,
   gero, girlo, girón, goirils, Gute erve, herb, herén, herp, hiero,
